teddy bear ( danish : 10 timer til paradis , " 10 hours to paradise " ) is a 2012 danish film starring kim kold as a danish bodybuilder who travels to thailand to find love . the film was directed by mads matthiesen and written by matthiesen and martin zandvliet . teddy bear is based on matthiesen 's 2007 short film dennis , which starred kold in the same role .